Which of the following directories contains configuration for UFW?
A)  /etc/ufwd
B)  /etc/ufw.d
C)  /etc/ufw
D)  /etc/ufirewall
C
C. The directory /etc/ufw typically contains configuration information for UFW. Onmany systems, /etc/default/ufw will also contain commonly changed default configu-ration items.208Appendix  Answers to the Review Questions
